on select me
  [  0] pusharglist 0 ........................... <>
  [  2] thebuiltin 318 .......................... <the doubleClick>
  [  5] jmpifz [ 47] ............................ if the doubleClick then
  [  8] pushsymb 4 .............................. <#room>
  [ 10] pusharglist 1 ........................... <#room>
  [ 12] extcall 5 ............................... <getThread(#room)>
  [ 14] pusharglist 1 ........................... <getThread(#room)>
  [ 16] objcall 6 ............................... <getThread(#room).getComponent()>
  [ 18] pusharglist 1 ........................... <getThread(#room).getComponent()>
  [ 20] objcall 106 ............................. <getThread(#room).getComponent().getRoomConnection()>
  [ 22] pushcons 1 .............................. <"SETSTUFFDATA">
  [ 24] pushsymb 146 ............................ <#string>
  [ 26] getparam 0 .............................. <me>
  [ 28] pusharglist 1 ........................... <me>
  [ 30] objcall 7 ............................... <me.getID()>
